  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EndingSceneController
  titleText: {fileID: 1031225239}
  storyText: {fileID: 1031225239}
  restartButton: {fileID: 442401593}
  uiCanvasGroup: {fileID: 0}
  endingTitle: '"ENDING 2: TAKEN IN BY STRANGER" '
  endingStory: 'Ending 2 : Taken In - A Cautious Welcome


    Exhausted and wary,
    Primrose barely has the energy to lift her head as a stranger approaches. But
    instead of shooing her away, the stranger offers a soft voice and a gentle hand.
    She is carried into a warm, quiet home, much different to the cold pavement she
    knows. Though she is safe from the streets now, the fear still lives in her eyes.
    It will take time, patience, and love to teach her heart to trust again.

'
